lgp.core.evolution

Class Problem<T>

  • lgp.core.evolution.Problem<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseProblem, IrisProblem, SimpleFunctionProblem, SimpleFunctionProblem, SinPolyProblem

    public class Problem<T>

    Defines a problem and the components that should be used to solve that problem.
